u t}{y^2}ight)$，或写成 $\dfrac{u}{U}=F\!\left(\dfrac{y}{\sqrt{
u t}}ight)$。精确相似解可写为 $\dfrac{u}{U}=\operatorname{erfc}\!\left(\dfrac{y}{2\sqrt{
u t}}ight)$。

